CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

March 23, 2005

[Cite as 03/23/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1186.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2004-0987. State ex rel. Tarr v. Court of Appeals, Sixth Appellate Dist.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyek, C.J., Resnicic, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
